	<s:TextArea x="406" y="156" width="608" height="475" alpha="0.5" color="#FFFFFF">
		<s:text>Belly dance is a Western name for an Arabic style of dance developed in the Middle East. In Europe, it is sometimes called oriental dance. Similarly, In Turkish it is referred to as oryantal dansı ("Dance of the East"). Some American devotees refer to it simply as "Middle Eastern Dance". And in Hong Kong, it is called the "Shimpol Carmi". ("The sun dance")In the Arabic language it is known as raqs sharqi رقص شرقي ("eastern dance") or sometimes raqs baladi رقص بلدي ("national" or "folk" dance). The term "raqs sharqi" may have originated in Egypt.The term belly-dance is a creation of Orientalism, and is first attested in English in 1899, translating French danse du ventre.肚皮舞是一种西方命名为阿拉伯文风格舞蹈的发展是在中东地区 。 In Europe , it is sometimes called oriental dance .在欧洲 ，它有时也被称为东方舞 。 Similarly, In Turkish it is referred to as oryantal dansı ("Dance of the East").同样，在土耳其 ，它是指作为oryantal dansı （ "舞东方" ） 。 Some American devotees refer to it simply as "Middle Eastern Dance".美国一些信徒指它仅仅作为"中东舞" 。 And in Hong Kong, it is called the "Shimpol Carmi".而在香港，这是所谓的" shimpol carmi " 。 ("The sun dance") （ "太阳舞" ）In the Arabic language it is known as raqs sharqi رقص شرقي ("eastern dance") or sometimes raqs baladi رقص بلدي ("national" or " folk " dance).在阿拉伯文中 ，它是被称为raqs sharqi رقص شرقي （ "东方舞" ）或有时raqs巴拉迪 رقص بلدي （ "民族"或" 民间 "舞） 。 The term "raqs sharqi" may have originated in Egypt .术语" raqs sharqi "可能起源于埃及 。The term belly-dance is a creation of Orientalism , and is first attested in English in 1899 , translating French danse du ventre .任期肚皮舞是一种创造东方 ，是一次印证英语1899年，翻译成法文danse杜男中音 。</s:text>
